you wanna get a riper one.

30:37.833 --> 30:41.817
Dr. Matt Lederman and his wife,
Dr. Alona Pulde,

30:41.837 --> 30:44.320
are among a small but growing
number of physicians

30:44.340 --> 30:47.323
who use a whole foods,
plant-based diet

30:47.343 --> 30:49.825
as a primary treatment
for their patients.

30:49.845 --> 30:51.827
From shopping with
patients to teach them

30:51.847 --> 30:53.329
how to read nutrition labels...

30:53.349 --> 30:54.330
And I don't care what it says

30:54.350 --> 30:56.332
on the front, the
back, or the sides...

30:56.352 --> 30:57.353
both: Look at the ingredients.

30:57.853 --> 30:58.834
And that's all I care about.

30:58.854 --> 31:01.337
To showing patients
how to prepare meals,

31:01.357 --> 31:04.340
they are not your typical m.D.S.

31:04.360 --> 31:07.343
Doctors Lederman and Pulde
use food as treatment

31:07.363 --> 31:10.346
because they feel it's the
